  <!-- FAQ SECTION -->
  <section class="faq-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

      <div class="faq-container">
        <div class="faq-item active">
          <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
            <span>How much do dental implants cost in Vietnam?</span>
            <span class="faq-toggle">▼</span>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">From $700 AUD for a single Straumann or Nobel Biocare implant, compared to $2,500+ in Australia. The cost includes the implant, abutment, and crown placement. All prices are transparent with no hidden fees.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
            <span>What implant brands do you use?</span>
            <span class="faq-toggle">▼</span>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">We use Straumann (Switzerland), Nobel Biocare (Sweden), Osstem (South Korea), and Dentium (South Korea) — the same international brands used in Australia. All implants come with manufacturer warranties.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
            <span>Is it safe to get dental implants in Vietnam?</span>
            <span class="faq-toggle">▼</span>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">Yes, absolutely. Our clinics are JCI-accredited and follow international standards. We have a 97.8% implant success rate with 10+ year longevity. Our surgeons have 10+ years experience and we use state-of-the-art 3D imaging for precision placement.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
            <span>How long does the implant process take?</span>
            <span class="faq-toggle">▼</span>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">Implant placement takes 1–3 hours. Bone integration (osseointegration) takes 3–6 months. Final crown fitting takes 2–3 weeks after integration. You can fly home 7–10 days after placement. Total timeline: 6–9 months for full completion.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
            <span>Can I fly home after implant placement?</span>
            <span class="faq-toggle">▼</span>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">Yes, you can safely fly 7–10 days after implant placement. We provide detailed post-op care instructions, pain management, and 24/7 WhatsApp support. Many patients combine their dental treatment with a vacation.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
            <span>What if something goes wrong after I return to Australia?</span>
            <span class="faq-toggle">▼</span>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">We provide lifetime remote support via WhatsApp with our surgeons. Your Australian dentist can also manage routine care. Our treatment guarantee and implant warranty cover any complications. We're always here for you.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
            <span>How do I know I'll get good results?</span>
            <span class="faq-toggle">▼</span>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">We start with a free 3D treatment plan sent within 24 hours. You approve the plan before any work begins. Plus, 4.9/5 from 100K+ verified patients means real results. Our clinics are transparent — no surprises.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
            <span>Do I need a visa for Vietnam?</span>
            <span class="faq-toggle">▼</span>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">Australian citizens can get a 90-day tourist visa on arrival, or an e-visa online. We help coordinate all logistics — airport pickup, accommodation recommendations, and post-op care arrangements.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
            <span>How much should I budget for flights and hotels?</span>
            <span class="faq-toggle">▼</span>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">Flights from Sydney to Ho Chi Minh City: ~$400–$800 AUD. 4-star hotels: $50–$100 AUD/night. Budget $1,500–$2,500 AUD total for a 2-week trip. Still a huge saving vs Australian treatment.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
            <span>What's the first step?</span>
            <span class="faq-toggle">▼</span>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">Fill out the form below with your details and photo of your teeth. We'll prepare a free custom treatment plan within 24 hours. Then you can decide if it's right for you. No obligation, no cost.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

